  <entry>
    <title>自动化测试</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/17/test/%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/17/test/%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="什么是自动化测试"><a href="#什么是自动化测试" class="headerlink" title="什么是自动化测试"></a>什么是自动化测试</h2><p>自动化测试（Automated Testing）是指使用专门的测试工具和框架，通过脚本或程序自动执行测试用例、验证结果并生成测试报告的过程。相比手动测试，自动化测试具有<strong>可重复、高效率、覆盖广</strong>的特点。</p><h3 id="核心价值"><a href="#核心价值" class="headerlink" title="核心价值"></a>核心价值</h3><ul><li><strong>提高效率</strong>：一次编写，多次执行，大幅减少重复劳动</li><li><strong>快速反馈</strong>：集成到 CI&#x2F;CD 流程中，问题早发现早修复</li><li><strong>保证质量</strong>：减少人为错误，测试覆盖更全面</li><li><strong>节省成本</strong>：长期来看，降低测试人力成本</li></ul><hr><h2 id="测试金字塔"><a href="#测试金字塔" class="headerlink" title="测试金字塔"></a>测试金字塔</h2><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><span class="hljs-code">        /\</span><br><span class="hljs-code">       /  \</span><br><span class="hljs-code">      / E2E \      端到端测试（数量少，执行慢）</span><br><span class="hljs-code">     /------\</span><br><span class="hljs-code">    /        \</span><br><span class="hljs-code">   /  集成测试  \    集成测试（适中数量）</span><br><span class="hljs-code">  /------------\</span><br><span class="hljs-code"> /              \</span><br><span class="hljs-section">/    单元测试      \   单元测试（数量多，执行快）</span><br><span class="hljs-section">------------------</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-单元测试（Unit-Testing）"><a href="#1-单元测试（Unit-Testing）" class="headerlink" title="1. 单元测试（Unit Testing）"></a>1. 单元测试（Unit Testing）</h3><p>测试最小可测试单元（函数、方法、类），特点是<strong>快速、独立、覆盖率高</strong>。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-comment">// Jest 示例</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">add</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a, b</span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a + b;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-title function_">test</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;adds two numbers&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-title function_">expect</span>(<span class="hljs-title function_">add</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>)).<span class="hljs-title function_">toBe</span>(<span class="hljs-number">5</span>);<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>常用框架：</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>语言</th><th>框架</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>JavaScript</td><td>Jest, Mocha, Vitest</td></tr><tr><td>Python</td><td>pytest, unittest</td></tr><tr><td>Java</td><td>JUnit, TestNG</td></tr><tr><td>Go</td><td>testing (内置)</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="2-集成测试（Integration-Testing）"><a href="#2-集成测试（Integration-Testing）" class="headerlink" title="2. 集成测试（Integration Testing）"></a>2. 集成测试（Integration Testing）</h3><p>测试多个模块之间的交互，验证组件间的接口是否正确。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-comment">// 测试 API 与数据库的交互</span><br><span class="hljs-title function_">test</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;user registration flows correctly&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-title function_">async</span> () =&gt; &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> user = <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">createUser</span>(&#123; <span class="hljs-attr">email</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;test@example.com&#x27;</span> &#125;);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> found = <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">findUserByEmail</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;test@example.com&#x27;</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-title function_">expect</span>(found.<span class="hljs-property">id</span>).<span class="hljs-title function_">toBe</span>(user.<span class="hljs-property">id</span>);<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-端到端测试（E2E-Testing）"><a href="#3-端到端测试（E2E-Testing）" class="headerlink" title="3. 端到端测试（E2E Testing）"></a>3. 端到端测试（E2E Testing）</h3><p>模拟真实用户行为，从前端到后端完整测试整个流程。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-comment">// Playwright 示例</span><br><span class="hljs-title function_">test</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;login and navigate to dashboard&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-title function_">async</span> (&#123; page &#125;) =&gt; &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> page.<span class="hljs-title function_">goto</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/login&#x27;</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> page.<span class="hljs-title function_">fill</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;[name=&quot;email&quot;]&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;user@example.com&#x27;</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> page.<span class="hljs-title function_">fill</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;[name=&quot;password&quot;]&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;password123&#x27;</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> page.<span class="hljs-title function_">click</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;button[type=&quot;submit&quot;]&#x27;</span>);<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">await</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">expect</span>(page).<span class="hljs-title function_">toHaveURL</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/dashboard&#x27;</span>);<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>常用工具：</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Playwright</strong> - 微软出品，支持多浏览器，API 友好</li><li><strong>Cypress</strong> - 开发者体验好，调试方便</li><li><strong>Selenium</strong> - 老牌工具，生态成熟</li><li><strong>Puppeteer</strong> - Chrome 官方头文件浏览器控制库</li></ul><hr><h2 id="测试最佳实践"><a href="#测试最佳实践" class="headerlink" title="测试最佳实践"></a>测试最佳实践</h2><h3 id="✅-应该做的"><a href="#✅-应该做的" class="headerlink" title="✅ 应该做的"></a>✅ 应该做的</h3><ol><li><p><strong>命名清晰</strong>：测试名称应描述预期行为</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 不好</span><br><span class="hljs-title function_">test</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;test1&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> &#123; ... &#125;);<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 好</span><br><span class="hljs-title function_">test</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;returns empty array when input is null&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> &#123; ... &#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>保持独立</strong>：测试之间不应有依赖关系</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-comment">// 每个测试应该可以独立运行</span><br><span class="hljs-title function_">beforeEach</span>(<span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 重置状态</span><br>  database.<span class="hljs-title function_">clear</span>();<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>使用 AAA 模式</strong>：Arrange（准备）→ Act（执行）→ Assert（断言）</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-title function_">test</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;calculates total correctly&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// Arrange</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> items = [&#123; <span class="hljs-attr">price</span>: <span class="hljs-number">10</span> &#125;, &#123; <span class="hljs-attr">price</span>: <span class="hljs-number">20</span> &#125;];<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// Act</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> total = <span class="hljs-title function_">calculateTotal</span>(items);<br><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// Assert</span><br>  <span class="hljs-title function_">expect</span>(total).<span class="hljs-title function_">toBe</span>(<span class="hljs-number">30</span>);<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>测试边界条件</strong>：空值、null、极大&#x2F;极小值、特殊字符</p></li><li><p><strong>保持测试快速</strong>：单元测试应在毫秒级完成</p></li></ol><h3 id="❌-避免的陷阱"><a href="#❌-避免的陷阱" class="headerlink" title="❌ 避免的陷阱"></a>❌ 避免的陷阱</h3><ol><li><strong>过度测试实现细节</strong>：测试行为而非实现</li><li><strong>测试之间有依赖</strong>：一个测试失败导致连锁反应</li><li><strong>mock 过度</strong>：过多的 mock 会降低测试可信度</li><li><strong>测试数据硬编码</strong>：使用工厂函数或 fixtures 生成测试数据</li></ol><hr><h2 id="CI-CD-集成示例"><a href="#CI-CD-集成示例" class="headerlink" title="CI&#x2F;CD 集成示例"></a>CI&#x2F;CD 集成示例</h2><h3 id="GitHub-Actions-配置"><a href="#GitHub-Actions-配置" class="headerlink" title="GitHub Actions 配置"></a>GitHub Actions 配置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Test</span><br><br><span class="hljs-attr">on:</span> [<span class="hljs-string">push</span>, <span class="hljs-string">pull_request</span>]<br><br><span class="hljs-attr">jobs:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">test:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="hljs-string">ubuntu-latest</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">steps:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">uses:</span> <span class="hljs-string">actions/checkout@v4</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Setup</span> <span class="hljs-string">Node.js</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">uses:</span> <span class="hljs-string">actions/setup-node@v4</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">with:</span><br>          <span class="hljs-attr">node-version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20&#x27;</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Install</span> <span class="hljs-string">dependencies</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">npm</span> <span class="hljs-string">ci</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Run</span> <span class="hljs-string">unit</span> <span class="hljs-string">tests</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">npm</span> <span class="hljs-string">run</span> <span class="hljs-string">test:unit</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Run</span> <span class="hljs-string">E2E</span> <span class="hljs-string">tests</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">run:</span> <span class="hljs-string">npm</span> <span class="hljs-string">run</span> <span class="hljs-string">test:e2e</span><br><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Upload</span> <span class="hljs-string">coverage</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">uses:</span> <span class="hljs-string">codecov/codecov-action@v3</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="测试覆盖率"><a href="#测试覆盖率" class="headerlink" title="测试覆盖率"></a>测试覆盖率</h2><p>覆盖率是衡量测试完整性的指标，但不代表质量。</p><table><thead><tr><th>类型</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>行覆盖率</td><td>有多少行代码被执行</td></tr><tr><td>分支覆盖率</td><td>有多少分支（if&#x2F;else）被测试</td></tr><tr><td>函数覆盖率</td><td>有多少函数被调用</td></tr><tr><td>语句覆盖率</td><td>有多少语句被执行</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>合理目标</strong>：</p><ul><li>单元测试：70-90% 行覆盖率</li><li>关键业务逻辑：追求 100% 覆盖</li><li>UI 组件：更注重集成&#x2F;E2E 测试</li></ul><hr><h2 id="推荐技术栈"><a href="#推荐技术栈" class="headerlink" title="推荐技术栈"></a>推荐技术栈</h2><h3 id="前端项目"><a href="#前端项目" class="headerlink" title="前端项目"></a>前端项目</h3><figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs coq">单元测试：Vitest / Jest<br>组件测试：Testing <span class="hljs-keyword">Library</span><br>E2E 测试：Playwright<br>Mock 工具：MSW (Mock Service Worker)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="后端项目"><a href="#后端项目" class="headerlink" title="后端项目"></a>后端项目</h3><figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nix">单元测试：语言自带或 pytest<span class="hljs-symbol">/JUnit</span><br>API 测试：Supertest <span class="hljs-symbol">/</span> http-test<br>集成测试：Testcontainers<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="学习资源"><a href="#学习资源" class="headerlink" title="学习资源"></a>学习资源</h2><ul><li><a href="https://testingjavascript.com/">Testing JavaScript</a> - Kent C. Dodds</li><li><a href="https://playwright.dev/">Playwright 官方文档</a></li><li><a href="https://testing.googleblog.com/">Google Testing Blog</a></li><li>《测试驱动开发》- Kent Beck</li></ul><hr><blockquote><p><strong>记住</strong>：测试的目的是建立信心，而不是追求数字。好的测试让你放心地重构和发布。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
